REPORT zjqr0000.

INITIALIZATION.
  INCLUDE zjqr0000_frm.

START-OF-SELECTION.

  DATA: a TYPE i.
  DATA: b TYPE i.
  DATA: c TYPE i.
  a = 1.
  b = 2.

  PERFORM frm_add_num USING a b CHANGING c.
  WRITE:/ 'c: ', c.

  PERFORM frm_write_hello.